Our new tv show, My Kind Of Country premieres today and I could not be prouder if it. @mickeyguyton @jimmieallen and I had such an Inspiring time working with these incredible artists. Please do yourself a favour and watch them grow on their incredible journeys. Inclusion, diversity and representation is so important in our genre and these artists represent everything beautiful about country music. First three episodes are out now, streaming only on @appletvplus ❤️

The next three episodes of My Kind Of Country come out this Friday on @appletvplus ! Tune in to watch the remaining artists move through the workshop episodes, as we get closer to finding our next country music star. ✨
Thank you @glaad for an unforgettable evening. So much joy, courage and love in the room. ✨ #glaadawards

My favourite episode of My Kind Of Country was getting to take our remaining Artist through my Visual Storytelling Workshop. Not only did we get to work together in bringing out their unique creative expressions but I got to invite some of my favourite friends to help see it come together. Watch @cameronduddy @cathyhahn and Jay Joyce guest star on episode 6 of MKOC only on @appletvplus ❤️

Who will be country music's next big star? This has been such a beautiful journey, getting to see these artists grow week after week and I am so excited for all of you to watch the finale of My Kind Of Country. Tune-in to find out who wins it all, streaming now on Apple TV+ 💙

Happy 1 year anniversary to my dear Bronco. An album that in its creating, helped me through the worst year of my life and then in its release, gave me the best year of life. Thank you to everybody who has supported, loved and listened to it. It will forever be a dedication to all the beautiful Broncos out there breaking free. 

In honour of the one year anniversary, we have printed a limited edition of gold Bronco vinyl. Coming out record store day April 22nd! Swipe to the end to see✨and visit recordstoreday.com for ordering info xo OP

When we filmed the @rupaulsdragrace Wigloose Rusical episode over a year ago, none of us on that set could have imagined how sadly relevant and poignant it would be today. So when Mama Ru asked if I would join @leland in a performance of Built On Drag at the finale, it was a very easy yes. The so called ‘Drag Ban’ bill is just one of a record number of bills targeting the LGBTQIA+ community this year. Please check out the ACLU’s website for info on how you can donate to the Drag Defence Fund and help. ❤️

The Southern spring tour is over and I am eternally grateful for the fact that I get to work and travel with my best friends.  This tour wouldn’t have been nearly as special if it wasn’t for our dear pal @marciii opening the show for us every night and most importantly the incredible drag talents of @missalexianoelle of Nashville, Tennessee and @alvi_dav of Richmond, Virginia. Having these queens performing during the set gave all of us in the band a sense of bigger purpose and pride, during a time when so many LGBTQ rights are being attacked. Thank you for sharing our stage and doing what you do best. ✨

Hey y’all, I wanted to extend a big thanks for all the incredibly moving and supportive comments & messages I have received from you all over the last week. I have been touring for 17 years this year (!) and I have never once cancelled a show in all that time, so making the decision to take time off was not easy. But I do believe we should be normalizing and have compassion for all of us to take a little step back when work and life become too overwhelming. I’m very much looking forward to writing some new music, visiting with friends and family and don’t worry, I’ll still be here yeehawing - just in front of a few less people for now XO all my love Op
Just saying howdy :) 🌾🩵

Some of my dearest friends in the world happen to be drag queens and today is International Drag day! Drag has always been at the forefront of activism, art and culture but currently these artists are fighting for their right to expression all across this country. Go out and support your local drag artists today (and don’t forget to tip ‘em!) ❤️🤠💅

Hey y’all! I wanted to jump on and thank you all for being so understanding and supportive over the last couple of months. I am doing so much better already and am immensely grateful for the ability to put my mental health first. 

We will be back on the road soon and we are working hard to rebook every city that we had to post-pone (along with many others)!

That being said, I am announcing something very exciting in a couple of weeks so be on the look out 
🐎🐎🐎 

i love you all and am so grateful for you

Happy Trails
xo

@glsen plays such an important role in providing safety, encouragement and shaping the future of our youth. In our current political environment, protecting LGBTQIA+ students is more important than ever and GLSEN has long been at the forefront of this fight. I’m honoured and humbled to be recognized by GLSEN this year at their Rise Up LA benefit, and we invite you to join me and GLSEN on October 28th to show your support ❤️ 

http://riseupla.glsen.org
Excited to share that y’all can now join me on the road to a good night’s sleep, in my @calm original sleep story, ‘Tales From The CB Radio’. Head over to Calm and take a snooze 😌

What an incredibly special evening with @glsen this past Saturday. Hearing the touching stories, speeches and honours from the evening made me feel very humbled and especially grateful to receive this years Champion award. The evening was made all the more special by my beautiful bestie @noahcyrus for presenting the award and my dear parents attending the ceremony. Thank you @glsen and keep up the important work ❤️

On a personal level, 2023 unexpectedly turned out to be the hardest year of my life. It was also a year filled with some of the most amazing moments of my career. I am so grateful to my friends, family, my band and crew for everything they do, and grateful to y’all for listening to my tunes. I hope everybody is as excited about 2024 as I am. Happy New Year yall, it’s gonna be the best one yet. 🐎💫
